<h1>闻</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">wén</span><span class=alesi>(wen2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 闻 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 闻</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/hear" style="color:black;">hear</a>; <a href="/dictionary/smell" style="color:black;">smell</a>; <a href="/dictionary/make" style="color:black;">make</a> known; news</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 9<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 9 strokes: <a href="/character/是" title="shi4: indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that">是</a>, <a href="/character/说" title="shuo1: speak, say, talk; scold, upbraid">说</a>, <a href="/character/要" title="yao4: necessary, essential; necessity">要</a>, <a href="/character/种" title="zhong3: seed; race, breed; to plant">种</a>, <a href="/character/面" title="mian4: face; surface; plane; side, dimension">面</a>, <a href="/character/看" title="kan4: look, see; examine, scrutinize">看</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/点" title="dian3: dot, speck, spot; point, degree">点</a>, <a href="/character/将" title="jiang1: will, going to, future; general">将</a>, <a href="/character/很" title="hen3: very, quite, much">很</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/門" title="Kangxi radical 169">門</a>&nbsp;169.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 3 <br><small>Other HSK 3 characters: <a href="/character/换" title="huan4: change">换</a>, <a href="/character/坏" title="huai4: rotten, spoilt, bad, broken down">坏</a>, <a href="/character/顾" title="gu4: look back; look at; look after">顾</a>, <a href="/character/酒" title="jiu3: wine, spirits, liquor, alcoholic beverage">酒</a>, <a href="/character/楚" title="chu3: name of feudal state; clear">楚</a>, <a href="/character/脚" title="jiao3: leg, foot; base, leg, foundation">脚</a>, <a href="/character/草" title="cao3: grass, straw, thatch, herbs">草</a>, <a href="/character/铁" title="tie3: iron; strong, solid, firm">铁</a>, <a href="/character/香" title="xiang1: fragrant, sweet smelling, incense">香</a>, <a href="/character/怪" title="guai4: strange, unusual, peculiar">怪</a> <a href="/char